    "7048141c-2f11-4621-ba5c-28f2f7eaf65e": {
      "type": "collapsible-content",
      "blocks": {
        "template--20128198459711__7048141c-2f11-4621-ba5c-28f2f7eaf65e-collapsible_row-1": {
          "type": "collapsible_row",
          "settings": {
            "heading": "That's not cheap!",
            "icon": "price_tag",
            "row_content": "<p>\"Not cheap! But worth every penny!\"<br/><br/>Our tankards are not cheap, and we take pride in that fact. Countless hours of hard work, dedication, and meticulous craftsmanship go into each and every one of our products.<br/><br/>Years of rigorous testing have been done to develop the perfect tankard – one that not only enhances your beer-drinking experience but also exudes timeless elegance. We pay the utmost attention to detail, ensuring that every piece is flawlessly designed and carefully constructed by skilled craftsmen who are incredibly passionate about their art.<br/><br/>So, when you purchase one of our wooden beer tankards, you can be confident that you are investing in a product of exceptional quality, built to last for years to come. We believe that the unparalleled craftsmanship and the love put into each tankard make them truly priceless.</p>",
            "page": ""
          }
        },
        "template--20128198459711__7048141c-2f11-4621-ba5c-28f2f7eaf65e-collapsible_row-2": {
          "type": "collapsible_row",
          "settings": {
            "heading": "Do you deliver worldwide?",
            "icon": "truck",
            "row_content": "<p>Great news! We are delighted to offer worldwide shipping on all our items.<br/><br/>Whether you're located down the street or across the globe, you can enjoy the convenience of having our exquisite rope handle beer tankards delivered right to your doorstep.</p>",
            "page": ""
          }
        },
        "template--20128198459711__7048141c-2f11-4621-ba5c-28f2f7eaf65e-collapsible_row-3": {
          "type": "collapsible_row",
          "settings": {
            "heading": "Can I collect my order?",
            "icon": "map_pin",
            "row_content": "<p>We offer the convenience of order collection directly from our workshop.<br/><br/>If you prefer, you can collect your order in person between the hours of 9am and 4pm, Monday to Friday. Simply send an email to info@chuug.co.uk along with your order number, and we'll be happy to arrange a suitable pickup time for you. This option allows you to personally experience the craftsmanship behind our handmade wooden beer tankards while saving on shipping costs. We look forward to welcoming you to our workshop soon!</p>",
            "page": ""
          }
        },
        "template--20128198459711__7048141c-2f11-4621-ba5c-28f2f7eaf65e-collapsible_row-4": {
          "type": "collapsible_row",
          "settings": {
            "heading": "Can you send the order directly to somebody else?",
            "icon": "heart",
            "row_content": "<p>Absolutely! We understand that you may want to send our exquisite handmade rope handle tankards as a gift to someone special. We are more than happy to deliver your order directly to the recipient's address. We will even include a gift message if you enter details in the \"Order special instructions\" box during checkout. This allows you to add a personal touch and make the gift even more meaningful. So go ahead and surprise your loved ones with a unique and beautifully crafted tankard, delivered with care and a heartfelt message from you.</p>",
            "page": ""
          }
        },
        "bc2d7b27-4026-4116-aada-d39a7402fe6b": {
          "type": "collapsible_row",
          "settings": {
            "heading": "How do I pronounce \"Chuug\"?",
            "icon": "chat_bubble",
            "row_content": "<p>It is pronounced as \"sh-oo-g,\" with a soft \"sh\" sound at the beginning.<br/><br/>The name was thoughtfully chosen to perfectly align with our business and products, drawing inspiration from the rich Norse and Swedish heritage. Just like the careful attention to detail we put into each of our handmade wooden beer tankards, the name Chuug embodies a sense of uniqueness and beauty. Join us on a journey inspired by Scandinavian traditions, and discover the exceptional quality of Chuug rope handle tankard mugs.</p>",
            "page": ""
          }
        }
      },
